1981.9-1985.7,majoredinfinanceinHunanCollegeofFinanceandEconomicsandgotthebachelor&rsquo;sdegreeofeconomics.
&nbsp;
1985.9-1987.7,studiedfinanceinShanxiCollegeofFinanceandEconomics,graduatedinJul.1987andgotthemaster&rsquo;sdegreeofeconomicsinDec.1989.
&nbsp;
1987.7-present,hasbeenteachinginDept.ofEconomics,Finance,CollegeofFinanceandBusinessinHangzhouUniversityandCollegeofEconomicsinZhejiangUniversity.
&nbsp;
Mr.TangisnowanassociateprofessorandmasterinstructorinDept.ofFinance,CollegeofEconomics,ZhejiangUniversity,mainlyengagedinteachingandresearchofMarketingandManagementofCommercialBanks,CapitalMarketandSecurityInvestment,TrustandLease,etc.,andespeciallyadeptinFinanceManagementofFinancialInstitutions,FinancialRiskAnalysisandControl,SecurityInvestmentandFinancialServiceInnovation,etc..Hehaspublishedseveralpapersinthefieldsaboveinnationallevelacademicjournalsandofferedfinancialbusinessanalysisanddecision-makingconsultationforChinaDevelopmentBank,BankofShanghaiandmanyotherfinancialinstitutions.
